        - Email is disabled on the PDI per AAP Section 0.7.2; this
          subflow honors that constraint.
        - When validation fails, the message is surfaced ONLY via
          Throw Error -> gs.addErrorMessage() -> form-level display.
          No email notification is generated for the requesting user
          or any administrator.

    NO-PII CONSTRAINT (AAP Section 0.7.2):

        - All comments, descriptions, and inline log messages avoid
          real names, real email addresses, real phone numbers, real
          organization names, and any other personally-identifying
          information. The error message references only abstract
          field names ("assigned_group") and the structural
